				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The Book of Restored Gods is a record belonging to the death god Jergal, containing the list of fallen and resurrected gods across the Forgotten Realms.\r\n\r\nCINEMATICS/MOCAP: The various methods of opening this book do not need to be shown on screen. There can be a close-up of the character focusing or a closeup on the book itself when it opens."
